nt/uploads/2024/02/gene_wilder_wonka-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格拉斯哥的一家唱片店单轨音乐店正在拍卖灾难性的威利旺卡体验现场的文物。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="361" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wonka-review-timothee-chalamet-3553138"><b>《旺卡》评论：蒂莫西·查拉梅在充满乐趣的节日盛宴中闪闪发光</b></a></li></ul><p>该活动<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/flop-willy-wonka-experience-in-glasgow-goes-viral-for-being-so-terrible-3593684">于上个月疯传</a>，其广告宣传为“甜蜜和想象力的庆典”，其灵感来自热门电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wonka"><i>《旺卡》</i></a>及其背后的罗尔德·达尔书籍。愤怒的家长在开业后不久就开始要求退款，称其为“牛仔”举办的“闹剧”。</p><p>该活动的组织者光明会之家在开幕仅几个小时后就决定终止活动。门票售价 35 英镑，承诺提供视听效果、奥帕伦帕舞蹈和巧克力喷泉，但实际效果只不过是一个几乎没有装饰的仓库，里面有一些塑料拐杖糖和一个小型充气城堡。</p><p>现在，格拉斯哥单轨音乐唱片店正在通过 Ebay 拍卖该活动的两个原始背景。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4OOuOIN4x3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-botto