w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3598795" class="wp-caption-text">杰西·乔·斯塔克。图片来源：眼镜蛇</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3598796" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3598796" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3598796" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Deadly-Doll-Launch-Party.-Credit-The-CobraSnake.jpg" alt="致命娃娃发布会。图片来源：眼镜蛇" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Deadly-Doll-Launch-Party.-Credit-The-CobraSnake.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Deadly-Doll-Launch-Party.-Credit-The-CobraSnake-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Deadly-Doll-Launch-Party.-Credit-The-CobraSnake-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Deadly-Doll-Launch-Party.-Credit-The-CobraSnake-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Deadly-Doll-Launch-Party.-Credit-The-CobraSnake-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Deadly-Doll-Launch-Party.-Credit-The-CobraSnake-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3598796" class="wp-caption-text">致命娃娃发布会。图片来源：眼镜蛇</figcaption></figure><p>另外，Jesse Jo Stark 发布了由制作人 F1LTHY（ <a href="/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a> 、 <a href="/artists/lil-uzi-vert">Lil Uzi Vert</a> ）和 warpstr 制作的歌曲“Patterns”的混音版。这首歌最初在她 2022 年的 LP“Doomed”中发行。</p><p> F1LTHY 和 warpstr 将“Patterns”转变为一首黑暗的舞池赞歌，在歌曲的合唱中添加了脉动的节拍，而史塔克鲸<em>则“Patterns，他们粉碎/Patterns，分散/Patterns，你粉碎/Patterns，Patterns。”</em> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="模式（F1LTHY 和 warpstr Remix）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WXeWfr4lWsM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌的发布是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">波斯特·马龙</a>在枫丹白露酒店首次跨年夜演出中为他的两场演出开场后发布的。斯塔克 (Stark <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jesse-jo-stark-wears-vintage-cher-outfit-to-bring-in-new-year-supporting-post-malone-3566365">) 在拉斯维加斯表演时穿上了雪儿 (Cher) 的 70 年代复古鲍勃·麦基 (Bob Mackie) 服装，以</a>时尚的方式迎接新年。</p><p>在其他消息中，斯塔克将踏上旅途，为<a href="/artists/the-veronicas">维罗妮卡乐队</a>即将举行的 2024 年哥特式夏季巡演提供支持，该巡演将于 4 月开始在美国各地进行。请查看下面旅游海报上的完整旅游日期，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-veronicas-tickets%2Fartist%2F1005682" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处获取门票</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0w5rO0v-Px/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.